Create a target group
And Create a Load balancer

Load Balancer require 2 Public Subnets in Different AZ for a VPC (Both must be public)
i.e Internet gateway must be attached to it 
and in both the Availability zones there must be an instance
Article on setup of application load balancer for instances in private subnet https://repost.aws/knowledge-center/public-load-balancer-private-ec2
